{"tid":1433034,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得女朋友好靚女","createTime":"2019-08-08T11:26:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T05:35:58.000Z","uid":201712,"like":3,"dislike":61,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"e2fa3e25dc8b1e6c432f74bd4714899a45086c33","tid":1433034,"uid":201712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:26:20.000Z","msg":"佢次次同親其他人出街都會好靚<br />\n單獨同我出街完全唔會化妝<br />\n<br />\n好多人溝佢<br />\n佢對我越嚟越差<br />\n到而家嘴都好少<br />\n<br />\n對住佢成日都有性幻想<br />\n佢真係好正但係佢對我好差<br />\n差到就嚟忍唔住<br />\n而家仲成日同人出去玩  去飲酒<br />\n<br />\n我應該點做<br />\n想分手但係又覺得佢好正"},{"pid":"71c94e1aa79a8b1b376eddd047190670eeead049","tid":1433034,"uid":53413,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:27:25.000Z","msg":"中出即飛"},{"pid":"1393bd8ce83d7544da67ced2cea04eee31c5e142","tid":1433034,"uid":17607,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:28:44.000Z","msg":"核彈都唔割席"},{"pid":"3a65a3746426582d61665c63f6118132df9391e8","tid":1433034,"uid":201712,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:28:45.000Z","msg":"冇得搞 咩都冇"},{"pid":"e96da0f78f52b54c5b2c1da9ee852e052121d6eb","tid":1433034,"uid":152040,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:31:35.000Z","msg":"準備戴帽<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8497389e637ffaa3dcd6f1fcc43f994ee55edcb","tid":1433034,"uid":126519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:34:01.000Z","msg":"搞左再講"},{"pid":"91086ad68265f8fb228e92adea0fb98f3407ff4c","tid":1433034,"uid":231079,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:35:01.000Z","msg":"帽事嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你訓醒就會發現其實佢唔係女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e690260343e9183f776454cb0efdcfd763fd26b5","tid":1433034,"uid":286700,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:35:46.000Z","msg":"圖呢"},{